  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Dark Cave is a gritty pixel art turn-based roguelike where you fight tense battles in opposite 3x3 grids against wave after wave of enemies.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/47a128fb9bed7562fff9f5ba587ad937.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement during battles is limited. You will need to carefully consider each move and anticipating monster movement positions is necessary. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a strategy that combines skills and movements to attack and defend yourself from enemies: anticipating the movement and attack patterns of every monster is key to your survival</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/bcdc6f451bc32f4b23624f0a839b689d.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=626 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select a hero from 3 distinct characters, each with 20+ available skills that can be upgraded multiple times</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 20+ enhancement effects, 20+ potions, and 40+ relics, forge your combat style through combinations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/fd7e72babfd94bb5d84aab25c7dab4db.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=626 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you finish a layer, the Blacksmith, the Angel and the Black Marketeer will bring you different items to help you on your journey. But sometimes you’ll have to sacrifice something in exchange for their boons… </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Dark Cave is a gritty pixel art turn-based roguelike where you fight tense battles in opposite 3x3 grids against wave after wave of enemies.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/47a128fb9bed7562fff9f5ba587ad937.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/f9fb40a4a56810d2a00a671639d373bf.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement during battles is limited. You will need to carefully consider each move and anticipating monster movement positions is necessary. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a strategy that combines skills and movements to attack and defend yourself from enemies: anticipating the movement and attack patterns of every monster is key to your survival</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/bcdc6f451bc32f4b23624f0a839b689d.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=626 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/1a2951ac44317a9ae56984d4d4df2fba.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select a hero from 3 distinct characters, each with 20+ available skills that can be upgraded multiple times</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 20+ enhancement effects, 20+ potions, and 40+ relics, forge your combat style through combinations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/fd7e72babfd94bb5d84aab25c7dab4db.avif?t=1753173604\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.poster.avif?t=1753173604\" width=626 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.webm?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758350/extras/c12c871f2246e747a62976f4611cf124.mp4?t=1753173604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you finish a layer, the Blacksmith, the Angel and the Black Marketeer will bring you different items to help you on your journey. But sometimes you’ll have to sacrifice something in exchange for their boons… </p></li></ul>",
